dict.string: Search, select and execute Fastlane lanes directly from Alfred

projectPath='{var:path}' workflowCache='{var:workflowCache}' command='{var:command}'
hash=$(echo -n ${projectPath} | md5)
echo -n "Caching lanes" cd $projectPath mkdir -p "${workflowCache%?}/projects" $(echo -n ${command}) > "${workflowCache%?}/projects/${hash}" echo -n "Done caching remote lanes"
tell application id "com.apple.dt.Xcode" set filePath to (get path of front document) tell application "System Events" to set parentFolder to POSIX path of (container of disk item filePath) end tell
